endpoint.Description: The API endpoint for Yandex.Cloud SDK client.

folder_id.Description: The default folder ID where resources will be placed.

insecure.Description: Explicitly allow the provider to perform "insecure" SSL requests. If omitted,default value is `false`.

max_retries.Description:
The maximum number of times an API request is being executed. 
If the API request still fails, an error is thrown.

plaintext.Description: Disable use of TLS. Default value is `false`.

service_account_key_file.Description: Path to file with Yandex.Cloud Service Account key.

token.Description: The access token for API operations.

zone.Description:
The zone where operations will take place. Examples
are ru-central1-a, ru-central2-c, etc.
